According to the [calcite official documentation](https://calcite.apache.org/docs/reference.html), the JDBC function needs to be escaped before it can be executed. We need to rewrite the SQL to the following format:
```sql
SELECT order_id, {fn IFNULL(SUM(cnt), 0)} AS totoal FROM (
	SELECT order_id, user_id, COUNT(1) AS cnt FROM t_order GROUP BY order_id, user_id
) a GROUP BY order_id;
```

